{"tid":130000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"捲盜卡案　IT男燒炭亡","createTime":"2017-02-22T05:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T03:09:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0be6feae8cebc491c976cb818f550f470aa471d4","tid":130000,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:11:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170222/19936100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170222%2F19936100&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7EkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=e58b87e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170222%2F19936100&h=39e7e692\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170222/19936100</a><br />\n<br />\n捲盜卡案　IT男燒炭亡<br />\n<br />\n6,697<br />\n ■男子留遺書燒炭亡，遺體由仵工移往殮房。<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n■男子留遺書燒炭亡，遺體由仵工移往殮房。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名電腦技術員疑捲入好友信用卡被盜事件，遭警方調查備受困擾，前晚在灣仔一單位內留下遺書燒炭自殺，救護員接報到場證實他當場不治，警方對案件正展開調查。<br />\n死者姓盧（34歲），任電腦技術員，據悉他數年前認識一名姓歐女子，兩人發展成好友關係，盧更租住歐女名下位於灣仔皇后大道東尚翹峰的單位。最近歐女發現其信用卡被人盜去，其間更遭盜用近100萬元，於是報警，盧曾協助警方調查，案中未有人被捕。<br />\n前晚10時許，大廈保安員巡樓時發現盧的單位冒出濃煙，於是報警，消防員到場破門入屋，揭發盧在睡房內燒炭自殺，救護員證實盧已當場死亡。警員在現場發現遺書，內容透露死念及叮囑歐女要好好照顧自己。警方事後撿走炭爐及手提電腦作進一步調查。<br />\n■記者李家傑  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n成報管理層稱遭跟蹤恐嚇<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n昨晚六合彩開獎結果"},{"pid":"cea29d81132eb6af6c9d590c7c2289fe4e16fa0c","tid":130000,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:12:49.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"816708ba99266de43c2afa6294b8eede3d2cb43f","tid":130000,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:16:05.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"5a63e1e98052ea9112d320d76369eebf85da6132","tid":130000,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:20:54.000Z","msg":"歐女幾歲"},{"pid":"4d46a5f396cd7a361beabd4bbfb14356558ca07c","tid":130000,"uid":65604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:38:08.000Z","msg":"真係唔好得罪IT男，歐女層樓即刻變兇宅。"},{"pid":"d03aa44345e7cd2e1355738ec86a83ff3103056d","tid":130000,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:40:08.000Z","msg":"姐係死者偷完條女卡碌左一球野仲係條女間屋到自殺?<br />\n<br />\n條女會唔會慘左D?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc10a12da2785d2731d993fcfa954a6dfec20eb","tid":130000,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:46:28.000Z","msg":"一睇就知條仔食拖鞋飯"},{"pid":"d68175efed0d5316f97183af49b30e072bc026cc","tid":130000,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:32:07.000Z","msg":"做咩唔訪問埋歐女呀 ?"},{"pid":"a15c6dd5928756dec8bb8a569106f8dcbf65e766","tid":130000,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T06:40:36.000Z","msg":"條女多得你唔少啦IT狗"},{"pid":"33965d5a3460a80666d1582cba70bd5d0a1d8e59","tid":130000,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T03:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}